<refsect1 id='description'><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para><command>gfmpirun_p4</command> executes a parallel command on filesystem nodes with
mpirun.</para>

<para><parameter>Command</parameter> can be specified by a gfarm-URL that is registered using
gfreg(1).</para>

</refsect1>

<refsect1 id='bugs'><title>BUGS</title>
<para>gfmpirun_p4 can only work with the MPICH-p4.</para>

</refsect1>

